deepin-terminal (6.0.6) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Feature:
      Optimized remote server functions
      Update window title according to current tab name
      New cursor type of bold underline
      New option to choose which special characters to be included in double
click selections
      Change opacity with "Shift+Ctrl+Mouse Wheel"
    Fix Bugs:
      Better implementation of enable/disable flow control feature
      Fix "Desktop Action" sections of desktop entry file to freedesktop standards
      Blacklist Noto Sans SignWriting fonts
      Fix compilation error
      Fix Shift+Tab shortcut is unusable in terminal shells
      Remove dependencies on dde-daemon WMSwitcher
      Remove useless desktop environment variable


 -- Yutao Meng <mengyutao@deepin.org>  Tue, 01 Aug 2023 16:37:36 +0800

